data.description: Looking for a spacious and open-concept home that truly has it all? This incredible property, which boasts a kitchen, living room, dining room, and office that seamlessly flow with one another. This fully upgraded home features top-of-the-line fixtures, hardwood floors, as well as granite countertops in the kitchen. This home features a bedroom on the main level with its own full bath, and 4 generously sized bedrooms on the upper level. In addition, the large upstairs media room makes this home perfect for movie nights or family game nights. With plenty of storage space throughout the entire house plus a full unfinished basement! The possibilities are endless. Situated near shopping options and schools as Mill Creek High School and Osborn Middle School. If you are looking for a beautiful and spacious home that offers the ultimate in comfort and style, make sure to check out this fantastic property today.
